  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    GDP deflators at market prices, and money GDP March 2019 (quarterly National Accounts)
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    This document contains the latest gross domestic product (GDP) deflators. The GDP deflator can be viewed as a measure of general inflation in the domestic economy.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

